Package by.bsuir.mycoolsite.dao.factory

Class DAOFactory

java.lang.Object
by.bsuir.mycoolsite.dao.factory.DAOFactory
public final class DAOFactory extends Object
Factory class for obtaining Data Access Object (DAO) instances. This class follows the Singleton pattern with a single instance accessible via getInstance().
